Arlington Asset Investment Corp. Cl A


            
            Arlington Asset Investment Corp. is a principal investment firm, which currently acquires and holds primarily mortgage related assets and holds certain other assets. The company's portfolio consists primarily of agency backed mortgage-backed securities and private-label residential mortgage-backed securities. Arlington Asset Investment was founded by William R. Ramsey in 1989 and is headquartered in Arlington, VA.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




